OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,FIt comes after an islander with
OL,7,Fchronic fatigue syndrome, which left
OL,8,Ftheir body feeling like it was
OL,9,Fshutting down, was deemed less
OL,10,Fincapacitated than someone who had
OL,11,Fsuffered the loss of a thumb.
OL,13,FCurrently, Long Term Incapacity
OL,14,FAllowance is based on what physical
OL,15,Fability a person has lost, rather than
OL,16,Fa deep analysis of how their condition
OL,17,Fhas affected their every day life and
OL,18,Fmental health.
