OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,FSandra Burt was diagnosed with
OL,7,Frheumatoid arthritis in 1981 when she
OL,8,Fwas just 20 years old and is unable to
OL,9,Fwork.
OL,11,FShe says: "It's a lot better now that
OL,12,FI have had so many joints replaced,
OL,13,Fbut before, when they said I wasn't
OL,14,Fold enough for joint replacement
OL,15,Fbecause I was only in my early
OL,16,Fthirties, it was very debilitating.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
