OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,F"Just getting out of a car or off the
OL,7,Fsofa or climbing stairs or anything
OL,8,Fwas incredibly difficult, but through
OL,9,Fkeeping relatively fit now, my
OL,10,Fmobility has certainly improved."
OL,12,FSandra continues: "To date, I have had
OL,13,F15 joint replacements, including my
OL,14,Fknuckles, ankles, knees, hip, elbow
OL,15,Fand shoulders.
