OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,F"It's massively important to receive
OL,7,Fsupport, because if you have a medical
OL,8,Fcondition, which means you can no
OL,9,Flonger work full-time, and you still
OL,10,Fhave a mortgage to pay on a very
OL,11,Fexpensive island, you need that
OL,12,Ffinancial support.
OL,14,F"Nobody chooses to have these
OL,15,Fconditions, so any financial support
OL,16,Fthat can be given to people, which
OL,17,Fmeans they can stay in work longer, is
OL,18,Fmassively important."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
