OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,FSandra continues: "Hopefully, the new
OL,7,Fsystem, which I have read the draft
OL,8,Flaw, will help in the future and be
OL,9,Fmore realistic and look at the bigger
OL,10,Fpicture, not just how far you can move
OL,11,Fyour arm or your leg, but look at your
OL,12,Fwhole life - your work life, your
OL,13,Ffamily life, your relationship.
OL,15,F"There is so much else involved with
OL,16,Fhaving a chronic pain condition, and
OL,17,Fusually general low mood if not
OL,18,Fdepression.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
