OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,F"It is difficult to work full-time if
OL,7,Fyou have a debilitating medical
OL,8,Fcondition."
OL,10,FDescribing how the condition first
OL,11,Fstarted: "It literally came on
OL,12,Fovernight in one of my shoulders, I
OL,13,Fwas signed off for a few days and
OL,14,Fgiven physio, but very quickly it then
OL,15,Fwent to the other shoulder and then
OL,16,Fthe knees, then the feet, hands, jaw-
OL,17,F everywhere.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
