OL,3,CJersey's chronic illness benefits set
OL,4,Cfor radical overhaul
OL,6,FOn what it was like to have to step
OL,7,Fback from full-time work, she adds:
OL,8,F"You worry you're going to lose your
OL,9,Fhouse, you have a mortgage to pay- it
OL,10,Fwas really quite a scary time.
OL,12,F"It was scary, very scary as a 20-year-
OL,13,Fold."
OL,15,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, Jersey's
OL,16,FSocial Security Minister, says: "We
OL,17,Fhave got rules that first came into
OL,18,Fplace back in the 1970s, and they
OL,19,Freally need modernising to represent
OL,20,Fthe modern benefits system for long-
OL,21,Fterm disabilities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
