OL,6,F"People won't see the benefit for a
OL,7,Fgood year or so, but it's important
OL,8,Fthat we have this enabling legislation
OL,9,Fin place."
OL,11,FThe proposed reforms will come into
OL,12,Feffect in the second quarter of 2027,
OL,13,Fsubject to States of Jersey approval.
